Reasoning: The paper deals with image recognition and learning a compact representation of images, which are common topics in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of a triplet loss function and metric embedding learning also suggests a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The study of social structure and distribution of a population, as well as the use of photo-id, may also fall under information retrieval (cs.IR) and multimedia (cs.MM).
